00:08:59.520 --> 00:09:02.880
them that the three of them can't ever be seen in&nbsp;
one place before they start to make out and sleep&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:07.360
together. This just proves that people aren't&nbsp;
always what they appear to be. Sam Lombardo,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:12.000
a respected guidance counselor, turns out to be a&nbsp;
manipulative schemer. At this point, it shows that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:16.080
he's the mastermind of getting money from Sandra,&nbsp;
and Kelly and Suzie are clearly under his spell.

