listen to what he has to say. Meanwhile, Ray stays&nbsp;
hidden as he records a video of Kelly and Suzie.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:59.120
Sam tells them to watch out for Ray before&nbsp;
reminding Suzie not to fall apart. When the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:04.160
call ends, Suzie accuses Kelly of double-crossing&nbsp;
her, but Kelly denies it then insults her. Even&nbsp;&nbsp;

